END

IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 446 // from: 445.0
SAY #41854 /* ~"Bet I'm going to be hearing THAT a lot." Morte clears his throat. "Let's see..."  'I know you feel like you've been drinking a few kegs of Styx wash, but you need to CENTER yourself. Among your possessions is a JOURNAL that'll shed some light on the dark of the matter. PHAROD can fill you in on the rest of the chant, if he's not in the dead-book already.'~ */
